data.description: So cute, impeccably maintained, brick English with 2 story addition(2020) overlooking Grennan Park! Owners bought this home to be their forever home and hate to leave. They thought of everything! You must see inside to see how large this home truly is! Walk into your bright and open living room/dining room combo with crown moldings and chair rails throughout the 1st floor, fully remodeled kitchen(2022) featuring huge center island, abundant cabinet space, quartz countertops, coffee bar, walk in pantry and huge hidden cleaning closet(within the cabinetry). The first floor also features 2 good size bedrooms, full bath, storage/closets, and much more, all with beautiful wood floors(waterproof bamboo) and a gorgeous custom staircase at the back of the home leading to the the private master suite. The Master Suite is drenched in sunlight by the numerous beautiful skylights and features a large sitting area, as well as an office space, full updated bath with soaking tub, walk in closet, plus additional walk in storage closet and separate heating and cooling unit. The full finished basement is complete with an in home theater, dry bar with beverage cooler, music studio, 3rd bath with jacuzzi tub and many good storage spaces. Every space in this home has been thoughtfully and meticulously planned out and the seller has paid attention to every detail. Whole home security system. Hard wired internet for computers/security. Home intercom system. Canned lights. LED lighting throughout. Your lovely yard features a nice get-a-way with low maintenance deck, pool(seller will remove with buyer does not want it) and large 2 1/2 car garage plus carport with fence that opens like a garage door off the alley.
